Synthesis

Pre-specified outcomes

  1. Maternal Death
  2. Liver morbidity (hematoma, rupture, failure)
  3. Acute pulmonary edema
  4. Acute renal failure
  5. Dialysis
  6. Platelet transfusion
  7. Perinatal death
